---
title: American-Style Chicken Schnitzel with Potato Wedges & Smokey Slaw
description: The classics have withstood the test of time for a reason and the pork schnitzel with wedges is one of them because, what can beat a crunchy and seasoned crumb? When served with potato wedges and a smokey aioli for dipping, this dish is unstoppable and we know that it will be returning to your table many more times.
